---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about melb.dev's mission, maintenance model, contact details, and security reporting."
>
  <article class="content-page content-page-wide">
    <div class="content-frame">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-black">About melb.dev</h1>
      <div class="about-layout">
        <div class="content-prose">
          <p>
            melb.dev is a curated directory of community-first technology events and groups. Our
            mission is to strengthen Melbourne's tech community and technical excellence.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our vision is to make Melbourne the best city in the world to build technology through
            technical excellence and a thriving community. We aim to support, not replace, existing
            groups.
          </p>
          <p>
            This website is built by the community, for the community: the source code is publicly
            available on its GitHub repository, anyone can report an issue, and approved
            collaborators can submit PRs.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you'd like to get in touch, contact our leadership team at <a
              href="mailto:gday@melb.dev">gday@melb.dev</a
            >.
          </p>
          <h2>Security</h2>
          <p>
            We take security seriously. Please email <a href="mailto:security@melb.dev"
              >security@melb.dev</a
            > with any security reports or disclosures.
          </p>
        </div>
        <figure class="about-visual">
          <img
            src="/images/melbourne-laptop.png"
            width="1000"
            height="666"
            alt="A laptop decorated with Melbourne-themed stickers, including a koala, coffee, tram, Formula 1 car, rain cloud, tennis ball, and football"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
